content.rendered:
BOSS AIR PORTABLE AIR COMPRESSOR

Boss Air Portable Air Compressor available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This is an outstanding evolution of the portable compressor.

What makes it so different is that it doesn’t rev its guts out and scream at you. Its quiet, its pumps up to 100PSI and is the perfect tyre checker/ inflater AND deflater.

Key features are;

  • Bright LED light so you can actually see what your doing at night.
  • Flexible tyre gauge for easy reading
  • Unique tyre deflator button.
  • Detachable air hose
  • Cigarette lighter attachment
  • Inflation accessories.
  • Convenient Blow mould Box

Specifications:

  • Voltage 12 Volt DC
  • Weight 2 KG
  • Max Amps 14 Amps
  • Max Working pressure 100 PSI
  • Displacement 40 Litres/Min
  • Cord length 3 metres

To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
